reviews.review_text:
Hamza This show can be found on Stash.nug.net.
Highly reccommend downloading it.
The road trips release sucks for the fact that they fade into the mojo jam.  Here you'll get the whole sequence.  Road trips also severely edited the "olin arageed" to 6 minutes. There's so much more to it, and is pretty awesome if you get a chance to download it.
